    "Id": "129770",
    "ThreadId": "39115",
    "Html": "Yes i have been able to get the autocomplete feature in the regular combobox, if i could use that in the datagrid it would be great. Can you please explain with an example asto how i can use a regular combobox in a DataGridTemplateColumn. I am not very familiar with it. I can add the autocomplete part by my self, i just need to know how to add a regular combobox in a datagrid using <span style=\"font-size:10pt;color:#a31515;font-family:'courier new'\">DataGridTemplateColumn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks...</span>\r\n",
