  {
    "Id": "129773",
    "ThreadId": "39115",
    "Html": "You can also go through DataGridComboBoxColumn.EditingElementStyle to set IsEditable and IsReadOnly.\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2008-11-03T13:33:25.563-08:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
  {
    "Id": "130200",
    "ThreadId": "39115",
    "Html": "Here is an example:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p>&lt;dg:DataGridComboBoxColumn.EditingElementStyle&gt;</p>\r\n<p>                       &lt;Style TargetType=&quot;ComboBox&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p>                           &lt;Setter Property=&quot;IsEditable&quot; Value=&quot;True&quot; /&gt;</p>\r\n<p>                       &lt;/Style&gt;                    </p>\r\n<p>&lt;/dg:DataGridComboBoxColumn.EditingElementStyle&gt;</p>\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2008-11-05T06:23:37.303-08:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
  {
    "Id": "130218",
    "ThreadId": "39115",
    "Html": "<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><div><span style=\"font-family:'times new roman';font-size:16px;white-space:normal\"><div style=\"padding-top:3px;padding-right:3px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:3px;background-image:none;margin-top:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;text-align:left;word-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><div>Hello Vincent Sibal,</div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Thank you for ur reply, I have put the following message in ur blog also.<br></div><div>The thing is that when i set the editing element style in DataGridComboBoxColumn, it only enables me to be able to type in to the combobox, it does not filter the items in the combobox to display only the items matching the text being typed... I have been able to get this done in a regular combobox using the code shown below. Could you please help me as to how i can get the same feature here in the DataGridComboBoxColumn, possibly by modifying the code below?</div>Thank you.</span><div><span></span><span style=\"font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px;white-space:pre-wrap\"><br></span><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\">myComboBox.ItemsSource = myItemsList;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\">myComboBox.IsEditable = true;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\">myComboBox.IsTextSearchEnabled = false;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\">myComboBox.Loaded += delegate</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\">{</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>TextBox textBox = myComboBox.Template.FindName(&quot;PART_EditableTextBox&quot;, myComboBox) as TextBox;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Popup popup = myComboBox.Template.FindName(&quot;PART_Popup&quot;, myComboBox) as Popup;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>if (textBox != null)</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>{</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>textBox.TextChanged += delegate</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>{</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>popup.IsOpen = true;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>myComboBox.Items.Filter += a =&gt;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>{</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>myItems selectedItem = (myItems)a;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>if (a.ToString().Contains(textBox.Text))</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>{</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t\t</span>return true;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>}</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>else</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>{</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t\t</span>return false;</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t\t</span>}</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t\t</span>};</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t\t</span>};</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\"><span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>}</span></div><div><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'-webkit-monospace';font-size:13px\">};</span></div></div></div></span></div></span>",
